 >
 > If the reduced dynamics are quadratic or multilinear, also write the reduced mechanism as a monomial hypergraph so the later exact audit knows which ordered source pairs are intended and which will count as spectators.
+>
+> If the goal isolates one role (for example, the trigger), state explicitly which surrounding roles make that label meaningful, and say whether the narrowed object is actually smaller than the predecessor mechanism.
 
 ## When to Apply
 

