 - **exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit exploration-001** — The next sharpening step was exactly this hypergraph move: treating Tao's mechanism as a directed hypergraph of quadratic monomials immediately turned a vague "near-closed circuit" slogan into a Phase 1-ready exact object.
+- **exact-ns-tiny-trigger-firewall exploration-001** — Trying to isolate the trigger as a smaller theorem target failed because the trigger role only had meaning inside the same five-role chain. The useful lesson was not "focus on `a3` alone" but "make the trigger-dependence on carrier / clock / conduit / output explicit immediately."
 
