+
+- The predecessor packet entry classifies the original near-closed Tao-circuit line as a `definition-level negative`, while this handoff framed the trigger mission as a `model-level negative`.
+- Resolved by keeping the predecessor classification on the original line, filing the trigger-specific terminal verdict in `execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/exact-trigger-object-not-standalone.md`, and updating the packet entry only to note that trigger packets inherit the same non-canonicity.
+
